{"type":"champion","format":"standAloneComplex","version":"4.15.1","data":{"Khazix":{"id":"Khazix","key":"121","name":"卡力斯","title":"虚空掠食者","image":{"full":"Khazix.png","sprite":"champion1.png","group":"champion","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48},"skins":[{"id":"121000","num":0,"name":"default"},{"id":"121001","num":1,"name":"机甲骑士 卡力斯"}],"lore":"卡力斯，一位凶恶虚空掠食者，悄悄的侵入瓦罗然，寻找这片大地上最富有生命能量的生物。每当他击杀一位牺牲者并吞噬他的力量后，卡力斯将会进化的更加强壮。<br><br>当卡力斯刚进入这个世界时，他是非常脆弱且饥饿的。然而，他初次遇到的那些弱小生物，并不足以满足他对进化的欲望。卡力斯为了达到目的，以自己的生命为代价去挑战、寻找极度危险的生物。每次的击杀与蜕变，都让他成为更加强壮、敏捷的掠食者。卡力斯开始进行肆无忌惮的攻击行动，相信他目前所拥有的力量是无人可敌的。直到某一天，正当他寻觅着美味的餐点时，他突然从一位掠食者变成了猎物。一道阴影自视野外扑出，以迅速的身影和钢铁般的利爪将他压倒在地上。眼前的咆啸与毫不留情的爪击，第一次让卡力斯见到了自己的血。由内而外的愤怒在此时爆发，锐利的刃划向这名猛兽的眼，迫使他退后。他们从日出对战到日落，直至死亡的气息逼近，他们才不情愿地各自离开。当他的伤愈合后，卡力斯萌生了一个想法，他要寻找能跟虚空之力相抗衡的对手并吞噬他。这股新生的动力驱使他开始了新的狩猎行动。总有一天，卡力斯会尽情的虐杀雷葛尔。<br><br>「进化，就是无尽的杀戮与吞噬。」<br>-- 卡力斯","blurb":"卡力斯，一位凶恶虚空掠食者，悄悄的侵入瓦罗然，寻找这片大地上最富有生命能量的生物。每当他击杀一位牺牲者并吞噬他的力量后，卡力斯将会进化的更加强壮。<br><br>当卡力斯刚进入这个世界时，他是非常脆弱且饥饿的。然而，他初次遇到的那些弱小生物，并不足以满足他对进化的欲望。卡力斯为了达到目的，以自己的生命为代价去挑战、寻找极度危险的生物。每次的击杀与蜕变，都让他成为更加强壮、敏捷的掠食者。卡力斯开始进行肆无忌惮的攻击行动，相信他目前所拥有的力量是无人可敌的。...","allytips":["- 当敌人因为身旁没有友军而被认定是孤立时，孤独的恐惧对这些目标的伤害会大幅增加。","- 当敌方队伍看不到卡力斯时，暗影杀机就会启动。可借由草丛或是虚空突袭再度启动。别忘了在有暗影杀机效果时向敌人进行普攻。","- 卡力斯可以自由地选择何时或何地才是他该加入的战场。为了胜利请谨慎选择战斗时机。"],"enemytips":["- 孤独的恐惧对被孤立的目标造成额外的伤害。因此在我方单位较多时，如小兵、英雄和塔旁会比较有优势。","- 掠翅飞跃和虚空突袭有比较长的冷却时间。卡力斯在这些技能进入冷却时，是非常虚弱的。"],"tags":["Assassin","Fighter"],"partype":"Mana","info":{"attack":9,"defense":4,"magic":3,"difficulty":6},"stats":{"hp":430.0,"hpperlevel":85.0,"mp":260.0,"mpperlevel":40.0,"movespeed":350.0,"armor":19.0,"armorperlevel":3.0,"spellblock":30.0,"spellblockperlevel":1.25,"attackrange":125.0,"hpregen":6.25,"hpregenperlevel":0.75,"mpregen":6.75,"mpregenperlevel":0.5,"crit":0.0,"critperlevel":0.0,"attackdamage":50.0,"attackdamageperlevel":3.1,"attackspeedoffset":-0.065,"attackspeedperlevel":2.7},"spells":[{"id":"KhazixQ","name":"孤独的恐惧","description":"卡力斯会自动标记那些因为与其友军有段距离的敌人，将之归类于被孤立的目标。孤独的恐惧除了对单一目标造成物理伤害外，对这类被孤立的目标将造成更多伤害。如果是使用<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化裂刃</span>，伤害更会大幅度的增加。卡力斯基础攻击和孤独的恐惧的距离会随之增加。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被动： </span>标记孤立周围没有其他友军的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主动： </span>造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 点物理伤害。如果目标被孤立，则伤害增加到 {{ e6 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a2 }}）</span>。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化裂刃：</span>如果目标被孤立，伤害增加到 {{ f3 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ f2 }}）</span>。提高卡力斯 {{ e5 }}普攻和孤独恐惧的距离。","leveltip":{"label":["基础伤害"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5],"cooldownBurn":"3.5","cost":[25,25,25,25,25],"costBurn":"25","effect":[null,[70,95,120,145,170],[30,30,30,30,30],null,[100,100,100,100,100],[50,50,50,50,50],[91,124,156,189,221]],"effectBurn":[null,"70/95/120/145/170","30",null,"100","50","91/124/156/189/221"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.2,"key":"a1"},{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.56,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[325,325,325,325,325],"rangeBurn":"325","image":{"full":"KhazixQ.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":240,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixQ0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixW","name":"虚空尖刺","description":"卡利斯发射爆裂尖刺，对周围所有敌人缓速并且造成物理伤害。卡利斯如果在爆炸半径内，则会获得治疗效果。如果选择 <span class=\"color00DD33\">进化尖刺拷问</span>，虚空尖刺会在锥形范围内射击 3 发尖刺，并且增加其缓速效果。","tooltip":"发射爆裂尖刺，对周围所有敌人造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 点物理伤害（对野怪造成 20% 额外伤害）并缓速他们 {{ e3 }}% ，持续 {{ e4 }} 秒。如果卡力斯在爆炸半径内，则获得 {{ e2 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">（+{{ a2 }}）</span> 治疗效果。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化尖刺拷问： </span>会在锥形范围内射击三发尖刺并且增加 {{ e5 }}% 缓速效果，持续 {{ e4 }} 秒。若被攻击单位为敌方英雄，则获得其视野，持续 2 秒。（不影响潜行单位）","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","治疗","魔力消耗"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ e2 }} -> {{ e2NL }}","{{ cost }} -> {{ costnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[8,8,8,8,8],"cooldownBurn":"8","cost":[55,60,65,70,75],"costBurn":"55/60/65/70/75","effect":[null,[75,115,155,195,235],[40,70,100,130,160],[20,20,20,20,20],[2,2,2,2,2],[50,50,50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"75/115/155/195/235","40/70/100/130/160","20","2","50"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.0,"key":"a1"},{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.5,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[1000,1000,1000,1000,1000],"rangeBurn":"1000","image":{"full":"KhazixW.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":288,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixW0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixE","name":"掠翅飞跃","description":"卡力斯奋身跳向目标区域，落地时对敌人造成物理伤害。如果施放的是进化技能<span class=\"color00DD33\"> 进化飞翅</span>的话，可以大幅提高飞跃的距离。当击杀英雄或造成助攻时，还可以立即重置掠翅飞跃的冷却时间。","tooltip":"跳向指定区域，造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 物理伤害。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化飞翅：</span>增加掠翅飞跃的距离。击杀敌方英雄或是助攻将会刷新掠翅飞跃的冷却时间。","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[20,18,16,14,12],"cooldownBurn":"20/18/16/14/12","cost":[50,50,50,50,50],"costBurn":"50","effect":[null,[65,100,135,170,205],[30,35,40,45,50],[10,10,10,10,10],[2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5]],"effectBurn":[null,"65/100/135/170/205","30/35/40/45/50","10","2.5"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":0.2,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[600,600,600,600,600],"rangeBurn":"600","image":{"full":"KhazixE.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixE0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":432,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"},{"id":"KhazixR","name":"虚空突袭","description":"每一个阶段都允许卡力斯进化他其中一项能力，赋予特别的额外效果。当启动虚空突袭时，卡力斯进入潜行并触发暗影杀机，同时增加移动速度。如果选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化伪装</span>，虚空突袭可以施放 3 次，并使卡力斯在潜行时受到的伤害降低。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被动：</span>当虚空突袭的等级提升时，卡力斯可以进化其中之一的技能。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主动：</span>潜行 {{ e1 }} 秒。启动暗影杀机可以提高 {{ e3 }}% 跑速，并且在潜行状态时无视单位碰撞。 虚空突袭可以在 {{ e2 }} 秒内再次施放。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化伪装：</span>可以施放 3 次虚空突袭，并且让虚空突袭的作用时间延长至 {{ e4 }} 秒。","leveltip":{"label":["进化","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e5 }} -> {{ e5NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[100,90,80],"cooldownBurn":"100/90/80","cost":[100,100,100],"costBurn":"100","effect":[null,[1,1,1],[15,15,15],[40,40,40],[2,2,2],[1,2,3],[50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"1","15","40","2","1/2/3","50"],"vars":[],"costType":"Mana","range":"self","rangeBurn":"self","image":{"full":"KhazixR.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixR0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":0,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"}],"passive":{"name":"暗影杀机","description":"当卡力斯不在敌方视野时，他会获得暗影杀机的效果，下一次基础攻击造成敌方英雄额外魔法伤害和缓速。","image":{"full":"Khazix_P.png","sprite":"passive1.png","group":"passive","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ASCENSION","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1036","count":2},{"id":"2003","count":3}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"type":"offensive","items":[{"id":"3078","count":1},{"id":"3071","count":1},{"id":"3181","count":1}]},{"type":"defensive","items":[{"id":"3156","count":1},{"id":"3068","count":1},{"id":"3110","count":1}]},{"type":"Consumables","items":[{"id":"2003","count":1},{"id":"2004","count":1}]}]},{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ODIN","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1036","count":2},{"id":"2003","count":3}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"type":"offensive","items":[{"id":"3078","count":1},{"id":"3071","count":1},{"id":"3181","count":1}]},{"type":"de